All other zeros $\rho=\beta+i\gamma$ of $\zeta(s)$ are constrained
to the **critical strip**, that is, they satisfy the bound $0<\beta<1$.
These zeros are distributed symmetrically about the line $\Re(s)=\frac{1}{2}$.

